data.name: Himasnhu Jangid
data.message: I am an electrician who has been working for more than five years, and I love to repair electrical items in the homes, like fans, washing machines, and meters. I am grateful for the opportunity to work for you. I would be honored if you would let me work for you. I hope you have a good day.
